      "type": "p",
      "text": "This is the first annual reassessment following DataSense's initial onboarding due diligence (March 2025). The initial due diligence was conducted under an accelerated timeline due to a business urgency request from Consumer Lending. Three items from the initial assessment were deferred to the Year 1 annual reassessment:"
